---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="雑誌エディトリアル — 地域おこし協力隊DAO">
  <div class="editorial">
    <!-- Nav -->
    <nav class="nav">
      <span class="nav-left">地域おこし協力隊DAO</span>
      <span class="nav-center">Magazine Style</span>
      <a href="#join" class="nav-right">Join →</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-col-left">
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span>Issue 01</span>
          <span>2024 —</span>
        </div>
        <h1>
          地域を<br />
          <em>編集</em>する。
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-col-right">
        <div class="hero-photo" style="background-color: #c8b896;"></div>
        <p class="hero-caption">地域おこし協力隊DAO — 全国の協力隊員がWeb3でつながるコミュニティ。株式会社あるやうむ運営。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Marquee -->
    <div class="marquee">
      <div class="marquee-track">
        <span>Community</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>DAO</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>地域おこし</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>Web3</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>協力隊</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>Community</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>DAO</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>地域おこし</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>Web3</span>
        <span>×</span>
        <span>協力隊</span>
        <span>×</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Story -->
    <section class="story">
      <div class="story-header">
        <span class="story-label">Feature Story</span>
        <span class="story-num">01</span>
      </div>
      <div class="story-grid">
        <div class="story-large-text">
          <h2>一人の隊員の挑戦が、<br />コミュニティの<br />力になる。</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p class="story-lead">地域おこし協力隊は、都市部の人材が地方に移住し、地域課題の解決に取り組む制度。全国に約7,200人の隊員がいる。</p>
          <p>しかし、多くの隊員は孤独だ。自治体ごとに状況が異なり、相談できる相手は限られる。同じ課題を、それぞれが別々に解こうとしている。</p>
          <p>地域おこし協力隊DAOは、この状況を変える。全国の隊員をWeb3でつなぎ、知恵を共有し、地域を越えて協働する仕組みを作る。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3 Columns -->
    <section class="columns">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="column-img" style="background-color: #8a9a7b;"></div>
        <span class="column-tag">Knowledge</span>
        <h3>知恵を<br />つなぐ</h3>
        <p>移住のリアル、活動報告、資金調達のコツ。先輩隊員の経験を、次の挑戦者へ。ナレッジベースとして蓄積し、誰もがアクセスできる共有知へ。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="column-img" style="background-color: #c4956a;"></div>
        <span class="column-tag">Collaboration</span>
        <h3>越境する<br />協働</h3>
        <p>北海道の漁村と四国の山間部。課題は違えど、根本は同じ。地域を越えて共通の課題に取り組む、クロスリージョンなプロジェクト。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <div class="column-img" style="background-color: #9b8c7a;"></div>
        <span class="column-tag">Governance</span>
        <h3>自律する<br />組織</h3>
        <p>DAOによる分散型ガバナンス。特定の誰かに依存しない、コミュニティ自体が自律的に成長する仕組みを設計。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pull Quote -->
    <section class="pull-quote">
      <div class="pull-quote-inner">
        <div class="pull-quote-mark">"</div>
        <blockquote>隣の自治体に同じ悩みの隊員がいたなんて、DAOに入るまで知らなかった。</blockquote>
        <div class="pull-quote-line"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Large Type -->
    <section class="large-type">
      <div class="large-type-inner">
        <span class="large-type-label">What is a DAO?</span>
        <p>
          <strong>Decentralized Autonomous Organization.</strong><br />
          分散型自律組織。ブロックチェーン上で運営される、中央管理者を持たない組織形態。全員が意思決定に参加し、透明性の高い運営を実現する。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section id="join" class="cta">
      <div class="cta-left">
        <span class="cta-issue">Next Issue</span>
        <h2>あなたの<br />物語を、<br />次のページに。</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-right">
        <p>地域おこし協力隊の現役隊員、OB/OG、そして地域に関わりたいすべての人へ。</p>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">コミュニティに参加する</a>
        <span class="cta-note">Powered by 株式会社あるやうむ</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <span>地域おこし協力隊DAO / 株式会社あるやうむ</span>
      <span>2024 —</span>
    </footer>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← デザイン一覧に戻る</a>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .editorial {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #f2ede6;
  }

  /* Nav */
  .nav {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 48px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(242, 237, 230, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .nav-left {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .nav-center {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #bbb;
  }

  .nav-right {
    text-align: right;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #C84B31;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-right:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 72px;
  }

  .hero-col-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 60px 48px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #aaa;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    color: #C84B31;
  }

  .hero-col-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hero-photo {
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 400px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-photo::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.8' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.1;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .hero-caption {
    padding: 24px 32px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #999;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  /* Marquee */
  .marquee {
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .marquee-track {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #ccc;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes marquee {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  /* Story */
  .story {
    padding: 120px 48px;
  }

  .story-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
  }

  .story-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #C84B31;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .story-num {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 200;
    color: #ddd;
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .story-large-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .story-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .story-lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 2;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #666;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Columns */
  .columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  .column {
    padding: 0 32px 48px;
    border-top: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
  }

  .column-img {
    height: 200px;
    margin: 0 -32px 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .column-img::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.8' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.12;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .column-tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #C84B31;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .column h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .column p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #777;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Pull Quote */
  .pull-quote {
    padding: 120px 48px;
  }

  .pull-quote-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pull-quote-mark {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 6rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #C84B31;
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: -24px;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    line-height: 2;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .pull-quote-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #C84B31;
    margin: 32px auto 0;
  }

  /* Large Type */
  .large-type {
    padding: 100px 48px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #f2ede6;
  }

  .large-type-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .large-type-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #C84B31;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .large-type p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    line-height: 2.2;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(242, 237, 230, 0.7);
  }

  .large-type strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f2ede6;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    padding: 120px 48px;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .cta-issue {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #C84B31;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .cta-right {
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .cta-right p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 16px 48px;
    background: #C84B31;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-note {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #bbb;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 24px 48px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #bbb;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #bbb;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #C84B31;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav { padding: 16px 24px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .nav-center { display: none; }
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }
    .hero-col-left { padding: 120px 24px 40px; }
    .hero-col-right { order: -1; }
    .hero-photo { min-height: 250px; }
    .hero-caption { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .story { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 0 24px;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .pull-quote { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .large-type { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .cta {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
